Summary: Star like object that blinked out then reappeared several times in a line pattern.
divs: sighting detailson 11\16\2010 at about 6:00 pm i was driving through the stephenville texas city park when i saw what appeared to be a bright star towards the south west. the star like object was in the direction of dublin texas, and slightly above the tree line. while i was looking towards the object, it blinked out. i then realized it was not a star. i brought my car to a stop and the object then reappeared, but in a slightly different location to the left. the object continued to turn off and on in a linear pattern moving from my right to my left. the object reappeared again in a few minutes but was lower and closer to the top of the tree line. i got my iphone 4 out and attempted to take video but the object stopped illuminating before i could activate the camera. i stepped out of my car and got my iphone ready to take video when the object reappeared for a third time. the first video attached below is what i caught on camera. the second video is of what appeared to be a military aircraft flying over about 15 minutes later. the military aircraft was coming from the ft. worth area (north) and was flying towards the dublin area at a high rate of speed. the first 3 sightings happened from about 6:00 pm to about 6:05 pm. the military craft flew over at about 6:15 pm. i started to leave the park at about 6:30 at which time i got a glimpse of the object again, but only for a brief moment. i stayed for a few more minutes and did not see it again. the object did not appear to be a conventional type aircraft. i did not hear any sound and could not make out a shape.
